title: What Should I Do After College? | Back To School

itunes:subtitle: I hate to say it, but back to school season is up…
itunes:summary:
I hate to say it, but back to school season is upon us. Some of us are going back, some of us just got out. Either way, the main topic is school and how it has affected our lives. A while ago I hopped on Skype with one of you, a listener, and here that is!  hope it helps some of you see some insight.
